N2  - The four essays comment on management research. Raghu Garud, Arun Kumaraswamy, and Praveen Nayyar discuss McGrath (1997) and state that the model focuses on exogenous technology development and boundary conditions, but does not consider coevolutionary dynamics. Rita Gunther McGrath defends her argument by referring to research by Garud and colleagues, tradeoffs concerning technological investments and amplification, and competitive interactions. Leon Leavitt comments on Bedeian (1997), Barry and Elmes (1997), and writing reports in the first-person singular.
