N2  - The article reports that a Theory Development Workshop will be held before the annual meeting of the Academy of Management in San Diego, on August 9, 1998. The workshop will provide feedback for drafts of theoretical work before they are submitted or resubmitted for journal publication. Discussion groups will be led by ?Academy of Management Review? board members. Selection criteria for the workshop and enrollment information is given, including the statement that no applications will be accepted after May 1, 1998. Loyola Marymount University professor, Peter Smith Ring, is the contact person.
